                <h4 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Awakening</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-soft-aura/80 bg-soft-aura/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-soft-aura/15">Morality</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-soft-aura/80 bg-soft-aura/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-soft-aura/15">Mindfulness</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-soft-aura/80 bg-soft-aura/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-soft-aura/15">Meditation</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-soft-aura/80 bg-soft-aura/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-soft-aura/15">Wisdom</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">The four pillars of Buddhist practice guide your inner transformation — from ethical living to the deepest wisdom.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Life Transformation card -->
          <div class="bg-white/[0.08] backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-7 border border-white/[0.12] hover:bg-white/[0.12] transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-morning-sage/25 to-soft-aura/15 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 border border-white/10">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-morning-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h4 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Life Transformation</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-morning-sage/80 bg-morning-sage/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-morning-sage/15">Purpose</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-morning-sage/80 bg-morning-sage/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-morning-sage/15">Health</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-morning-sage/80 bg-morning-sage/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-morning-sage/15">Soul</span>
                  <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-morning-sage/80 bg-morning-sage/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-morning-sage/15">Balance</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">Apply your awakening to every dimension of life — purpose, health, relationships, and soul work become one integrated journey.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Temple callout -->
