          <ul class="space-y-3 text-warm-charcoal">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-deep-calm mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span>Release stress, suffering, and restless thoughts</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-deep-calm mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span>Cultivate mindfulness, meditation, and inner awareness</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-deep-calm mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span>Discover the 347 path of awakening through Vipassana</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-deep-calm mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span>Live with calm presence and empowered peace</span></li>
